asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: DJ Baby Beats
description: Hey fluffle, Im DJ Baby Beats. Ive been influenced by a lot of talented artists in my time, such as The Fliggles, Fluffleme Street, Fluf School, Fluf Now, and After Fluf Skool.  I LOVE to play to my audience. In fact the reactions make me so happy, theres normally lots screaming and crying flufflets, they love me so much, I bring them to tears. But a lot of the time I am playing for the parents. Mama flufs and dada flufs used to party and still love to have a good time. And as they say, theres a time and place for everything. Thats when I bring out tracks from one of my favourite artists, Wattsson Music. I fan girl her hard. You can often catch me sucking on my pacifier. . . a relaxing and meditative experience, I find. The new FLUF pacifiers come with some tasty elixirs infused into the plant based rubber, so its a taste sensation too, and a great gift to throw out to parents if flufflets get out of control. I love to take my fans on a journey with my music, so my spend ages planning out my sets. As tagged, I am a FLUF entertainer, and bringing positive wybes to the fluffle tribe is my game.  I love you guys so much, thanks for supporting me, Im so excited for the future of fluf.world and cant wait to keep you happy n hopping. Fluf Life. Peace

name: Ether
description:
Lady Marianne Ether, or Ether for short, was born with a vision that was destined to change the world. With uncanny intuition, it is said that she has the ability to tap into an interplanetary network that connects all things. 

Known for her hypnotic charm, Ether built her name disrupting traditional financial markets in the city while spending her weekends driving fast cars. After spending one fateful night dancing in the shroomlight, she decided it was time for change. She now spends much of her time in the underground working on Mycelium based projects for the fluffle. 

It is often mentioned in whispers that she is one of the founding members of the Rabbit Island Pirates (RIP), a secretive society of FLUFs that are often seen wearing their distinctive pirate hats around the underground and beyond.

name: Bun
description:
His real name is Li'l Bun Buns but no one calls him that. It's just Bun, like the bread, only made of his favorite herb instead of grain. We don't know what kind of rabbit he is exactly, and he might seem like just another rabbit on the surface but there is more to Bun than meets the eye.

When it comes to talking about himself he never reveals much. He's a rabbit of mystery, but he is known to drop some juicy details on occasion. He's got a lot going for him, and he knows it. That much is clear from the way he struts around at the parties, always making sure everyone knows that he's there and why he's worth being around. 

The fact is he can be a bit of a loose cannon and will let you know it too if the moment calls for it. Laughing boisterously, making outlandish jokes, or shunning traditional fashion sensibilities by wearing nothing but his birthday suit (he's got the body for it), and basically being the life of the party is how he rolls.

He makes headlines every now again by smoking it up with Snoop Dogg and hotboxing the entire burrow, being a maniac on the dance floor to the banger tune Messiah at Fluf Haus, or getting wasted at the after-party and getting matching 'We Are Many' tattoos with Angelbaby. 

Bun is also smarter than your average rabbit. He knows the politics of the underground and how to navigate it without drawing unwanted attention. He knows how to get what he wants, who to talk to, and who to avoid. He can also get you what you want if he has it. If he doesn't, he'll put in a good word for you and maybe even hook you up with one of his connections.

We know that he's got a few girls in the mix, but no one is really sure which one he loves the most. We assume that they are all in his rotation, but there is one Fluf that he has a rabbit crush on. We don't know exactly who that one is but he has hinted that she is Bun's dream girl. She lives in the burrows, loves to smoke weed, and is totally cool with Bun's friends.

In short, he's a great rabbit to know because he always knows the best parties and really loves getting high, and he's always more than happy to share the weed with a friend. But he also has quite the temper which can be a bummer. Just yesterday he was at some poetry reading and we saw him jump up and sock someone dead in the face for heckling him. We love you Bun but you need to learn how to control that temper of yours!

Bun is always looking to expand his social network so if you're interested in getting some bunny love just shoot him a line at: lilbunbuns420gmail.com

So go ahead, hit up Bun. You know you want to.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
